                            <h4 class="center">Via CAR:</h4>
                          <h4 class="small">From Manhattan:</h4>
                          <ul>
                              <li>Take the Brooklyn Bridge or the Battery Tunnel to the Brooklyn-Queens 
                              	Expressway/Gowanas (RT. 278).</li>
                              <li>Follow signs to Verrazano Bridge and Staten Island.</li>  
                              <li>Exit at 86th Street * two exits before the bridge.</li>
                              <li>Take 86th Street Exit and <em>follow service road</em> to traffic light.</li>
                              <li><em>Make a right</em> onto 86th Street.</li>
                              <li>Go <em>three traffic lights</em> and <em>make a left</em> onto 4th Avenue.</li>
                              <li>Take 4th Avenue past 90th Street</li>
                              <li class="nobull">* you will see our building on the right corner.</li>
                              <li><em>Make a right</em> turn into the credit union's parking lot.</li>
                          </ul>
                          <h4 class="small">From NJ/Staten Island:</h4>
                          <ul>
                              <li>Take the Staten Island Expressway to the Verrazano Bridge.</li>
                              <li>Take the <em>lower level</em> of the bridge and <em>stay to the right</em>.</li>
                              <li>Exit at 92nd Street and <em>take the service road</em> to traffic light.</li>
                              <li>At the light <em>make a left</em> onto 92nd Street.</li>
                              <li>Take 92nd Street to 4th Avenue and <em>make a right</em>.</li>
                              <li>Take 4th Avenue to 90th Street (2 blocks).</li>
                              <li><em>Make a left</em> into the credit union's parking lot</li>
                              <li class="nobull">* just prior to 90th Street.</li>
                          </ul>
