                          <p>&nbsp;</p>
                          <ul>
                              <li>Take the Belt parkway West to Exit 2 (4th Avenue).</li>
                              <li class="nobull">* Exit leaves you on 4th Avenue and 102nd Street.</li> 
                              <li>Continue on 4th Avenue to 90th Street (12 blocks).</li>
                              <li><em>Make a left</em> into the credit union's parking lot</li>
                              <li class="nobull">* just prior to 90th Street.</li>
                          </ul>
